<paragraph id="8BAC3684FFEA973B70F9F9F9FF6DFF50" blockId="13.[677,1211,1649,1699]" lastBlockId="15.[112,647,215,371]" lastPageId="15" lastPageNumber="570" pageId="13" pageNumber="568">
DIAGNOSE. — La spermathèque de la nouvelle espèce présente un appendice extérieur sur le bulbe distal. Les espèces de 
<collectingCountry id="F3047614FFE8973B7280FF5FFECBFECC" box="[220,335,215,239]" name="Madagascar" pageId="15" pageNumber="570">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
qui possèdent un tel appendice sont 
<taxonomicName id="4C134D07FFE8973B72C2FF7AFE20FF2A" authority="Pace, 1999" authorityName="Pace" authorityYear="1999" box="[158,420,241,265]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Brachida" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="570" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="appendiculata">
<emphasis id="B967EA96FFE8973B72C2FF7AFEB3FF2A" box="[158,311,241,265]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="570">B. appendiculata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF824B75FFE8973B7360FF79FE20FF2A" author="PACE R." box="[316,420,241,265]" pageId="15" pageNumber="570" refId="ref9743" refString="PACE R. 1999. - Insectes Coleopteres Staphylinidae Aleocharinae. Faune de Madagascar 89. Paris, 261 p." type="book" year="1999">Pace, 1999</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, et 
<taxonomicName id="4C134D07FFE8973B739EFF7AFD00FF2A" authority="Pace, 2006" authorityName="Pace" authorityYear="2006" box="[450,644,241,265]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Brachida" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="570" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="janaki">
<emphasis id="B967EA96FFE8973B739EFF7AFD92FF2A" box="[450,534,241,265]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="570">B. janaki</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF824B75FFE8973B7046FF79FD00FF2A" author="PACE R." box="[538,644,241,265]" pageId="15" pageNumber="570" pagination="381 - 705" refId="ref9764" refString="PACE R. 2006. - Aleocharinae de Madagascar. Insectes Coleopteres Staphylinidae Aleocharinae. Faune de Madagascar 89, Supplemento I (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). Bollettino del Museo regionale di Scienze naturali di Torino 23: 381 - 705." type="journal article" year="2006">Pace, 2006</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. La nouvelle espèce se distingue de ces deux dernières par ses yeux réduits, un corps nettement plus trapu et par la spermathèque plus mince que celles de 
<taxonomicName id="4C134D07FFE8973B73B5FEC9FD03FF7A" authorityName="Pace" authorityYear="1999" box="[489,647,321,345]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Brachida" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="570" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="appendiculata">
<emphasis id="B967EA96FFE8973B73B5FEC9FD03FF7A" box="[489,647,321,345]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="570">B. appendiculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
et 
<emphasis id="B967EA96FFE8973B72D6FED4FF6DFF50" box="[138,233,347,371]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="570">
<taxonomicName id="4C134D07FFE8973B72D6FED4FF61FF50" authorityName="Pace" authorityYear="2006" box="[138,229,347,371]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Brachida" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="570" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="janaki">B. janaki</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
